WEBVTT

1
00:13:46.458 --> 00:13:48.598 
还真有其他时期[经期]的衣服呢
Talk about a period costume.

2
00:13:49.468 --> 00:13:51.698 
是啊  超恶心啊
You're right. It's disgusting.

3
00:13:51.698 --> 00:13:53.668 
我做不来
I can't do this anymore.

4
00:13:53.668 --> 00:13:55.668 
我要走了  我不想扮精灵了
I'm leaving. I don't want to do this anymore.

5
00:13:55.668 --> 00:13:58.418 
我身心疲惫同时又焦躁不堪
I feel tired and wired at the same time.

6
00:13:58.418 --> 00:14:01.298 
这个主意好糟糕  好糟糕  好糟糕  好糟糕
This was an awful, awful, awful, awful, awful idea!

7
00:14:01.298 --> 00:14:02.538 
够了  冷静
All right, calm down!

8
00:14:02.538 --> 00:14:04.788 
老天  你就像只圣诞抽风猴子
Jeez, you're like a Christmas crack monkey.

9
00:14:05.408 --> 00:14:08.168 
听着  我们哪也不去  知道吗
Look, we are not going anywhere, okay?

10
00:14:08.308 --> 00:14:10.718 
我衣服都穿好了  我们需要这份工作
You got me all elfed up, and now we need these jobs.

11
00:14:10.718 --> 00:14:11.998 
所以去找个人说说
So just go talk to someone

12
00:14:11.998 --> 00:14:13.968 
解释下你得换身新衣服的原因
and tell them why you need a new pair of tights.

13
00:14:13.968 --> 00:14:16.028 
我做不到  太尴尬了
I can't. It's embarrassing.

